{"word":"G756 - ἄρχομαι - árchomai - ar'-khom-ahee - Begin","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">árchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ar'-khom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Begin</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆளு"},{"paragraph":"1. to be the first to do (anything); to begin"},{"paragraph":"2. to be chief, leader, ruler"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice of <a href=\"#/G757 - ἄρχω - árchō - ar'-kho/757\">G757</a> (through the implication of <i>precedence</i>); to <i>commence</i> (in order of time): - rehearse from the) begin (-ning).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}